<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>نَكْسَة <span class="c4">[مفرد]</span>: ج نَكَسات ونَكْسَات:<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
